'''头部移植'''，是一种外科手术，其目的是将一个人或其他动物的头部嫁接到另一个的身体上。头部移植曾经在狗、猴子、老鼠等动物上做过实验，但目前尚无在人类应用的记录。<ref>{{cite web| title = The Future of Brain Transplants| work = NOVA| url = http://www.mymultiplesclerosis.co.uk/stranger-than-fiction/head-transplant.html| accessdate = 2012-05-11| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071120014343/http://www.mymultiplesclerosis.co.uk/stranger-than-fiction/head-transplant.html| archive-date = 2007-11-20| dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref name="NewTalk">{{cite web |url=http://tw.news.yahoo.com/神經學家-人頭移植已可行-但有道德風險-061055599.html |title=神經學家：人頭移植已可行 但有道德風險 |author=NewTalk新頭殼 |publisher=Yahoo!奇摩新聞 |accessdate=2013-12-23 |language=zh-tw |date=2013-07-03 |archive-date=2013-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015191607/http://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A5%9E%E7%B6%93%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6-%E4%BA%BA%E9%A0%AD%E7%A7%BB%E6%A4%8D%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C-%E4%BD%86%E6%9C%89%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-061055599.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>由于重新联接受损脊髓的医疗技术尚未取得成功，头部手术完成后的人处于[[四肢瘫痪|四肢瘫痪]]状态。<ref name = "time">{{cite journal| first = Charles| last = Krauthammer| authorlink = | coauthors = | title = Of Headless Mice...And Men| journal = Time| volume = | issue = | pages = | id = | url = http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,987687,00.html| date = January 19, 1998| access-date = 2013-12-22| archive-date = 2013-08-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130817171338/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,987687,00.html| dead-url = yes}} Discusses headless cloned humans</ref>

2013年7月3日，媒體報導[[卡納維洛|卡納維洛]]（Sergio Canavero）在《神經外科》期刊發表，認為只要能解決脊髓神經縫合問題，[[羅伯特懷特|羅伯特懷特]]（Robert White）對猴子頭顱的移植技術也就可以應用在人類頭部，對於脊髓接合問題則可利用「[[膜融合劑|膜融合劑]]」技術，膜融合劑有如[[聚乙二醇|聚乙二醇]]（PEG）等化學物質來融化、接合脊髓，但這樣的目標得再投入至少3千萬美金的研究，若研究成功則可為肌肉萎縮症、器官衰竭、癱瘓，甚至是癌症患者，帶來解決無法根治的難題而獲得重生。<ref name="NewTalk"/>此外，头部移植手术的伦理问题舆论尚未达成较一致的意见。<ref name="NewTalk"/>

